<h2 class="bold font-l">Airplane</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
During a Bar Brawl between two girl scouts, one of them is thrown down the bar and crashes headfirst into a jukebox, which starts playing &quot;Staying Alive&quot;. </p>
</div>
